# Title: Suspicious Extrac32 Execution
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2021-11-26
# Level: medium
# Description: Download or Copy file with Extrac32
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1105
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_extrac32.yml

CommandLine="*.cab*" CommandLine="*extrac32.exe*" OR Image="*\\extrac32.exe" OR OriginalFileName="extrac32.exe" CommandLine IN ("*/C*", "*/Y*", "* \\\\*")